Package honeyroasted.jype.system.solver

Interface TypeConstraint

All Known Subinterfaces:
ErasureConstraint, ForceConstraint
All Known Implementing Classes:
ErasureConstraint.Erasure, ForceConstraint.Capture, TypeConstraint.Bound, TypeConstraint.Equal, TypeConstraint.False, TypeConstraint.True
public interface TypeConstraint
This interface represents some sort of constraint over Types, for use in TypeSolvers. It is very general and each TypeSolver may define their own constraints and/or use the default ones. A TypeSolver is not required to accept every implementation of TypeConstraint, but rather only the ones relevant to whatever computation it is performing.
